channel.title: Project Fubergen Lite v1.2 Client [Cheats inside] Open release
channel.description:
This will be probably my latest public release of lite serie.
[size=8pt]next releases wont be public, ofc, you can download them via these lite version's updater[/size] About lite v1.2: Yes, this last lite version includes almost everything from previous project fubergen client features, like v1 to v8.3.2. And this is open source as always lmfao [QUOTE]Features:[/QUOTE] [ul][*]- All skillcapes, except hunter [*]- New loading and connection lost bar [*]- Jframe with menu [*]- Music in client (u can put your favorite music) [*]- New Hairstyles and clothes. [*]- Nonrenamed with 377 cache [*]- Fixed Prayer bug (freezed client, not enough) [*]- Port and ip Changer in menu [*]- Screenshot button [*]- Vengeance works [*]- More options for themes from client's icon [*]- Note:Choosing different themes? Just click Fubergen's icon [*]- All Previous version's features are in this version too [*]- new hp bar [*]- Chat filter [*]- Edited sprites [*]- Client tells, when update available [*]- music menu deleted, Music buttons added [*]- Custom crowns [*]- Scrollbar fixed [*]- Renamed Gui [*]- 3rd armours [*]- All God's swords [*]- Lots of custom items, recolored items [*]- Compatible with most delta servers [*]- And alot more[/ul] [b]Update history[/b] [QUOTE] Latest new in v4.2[/QUOTE] [ul][*]- Added fully working client's loader [*]- Stopmenu fixed...very simple [*]- System.exit thing removed [*]- Unzipper [*]- Updated music player [*]- Updated Gui.java[/ul] [QUOTE]Latest new in v4.3 beta[/QUOTE] [ul][*]- Updated Chatbox frame [*]- fixed some sprites [*]- New chatbox buttons(click areas + writing)[/ul] [QUOTE]Latest new in v4.3[not gonna release][/QUOTE] [ul][*]- Some Bug fixed [*]- deleted some unneeded things[/ul] [QUOTE]Latest new in v4.4[/QUOTE] [ul][*]- Added New Admin Crown [*]- Theme changer from v1.2 (Recustomized) [*]- ZOOMER [added back] [*]- Interface add-on: Buy 20 (Thx for Reaper) [*]- Updater in jmenu now [*]- Some prites from 4.2 [*]- Added noclip to jmenu, lol [*]- FileUpdater works now - Update From jmenu [*] [B][U]Explaining lil.[/U][/B] Fileupdater is new update for fubergen client that tells, [*] "if" theres new java/class files,etc for download and it tells the name of file[/ul] [QUOTE]Latest New in v5[/QUOTE] [ul][*]- Server Pinger [*]- Added Favourite servers menu[/ul] [QUOTE]Latest New in v6[/QUOTE] [ul][*]- Special thanks for Danno [*]- Ingame Hp Changer [*]- More Modern Add Models system [*]- Lots of features in Extra jmenu [*]- New gameframe with wings :d [*]- All updaters removed! [*]- Cursor[/ul] [QUOTE]News in V7 Alpha[/QUOTE] [ul][*]- 474 Gameframe [*]- Theres some new prayers [*]- Clickable buttons working [*]- Option tab working [474] [*]- Emote tab working [474] [*]- Equipment stat works [ you must modify in server side] [*]- buy "x" working [you mustmodify in server side] [*]- Log out door works [*]- Orb filling works [*]- Autotalker in client [thanks for bluur] [*]- Color changer [thanks for bluur] [*]- run orb isin't 100% perfect but works [*]- Clan chat [*]- New cursors [i fixed lil to make it work front of the jframe ] ( thanks for cocoa ) [*]- "add all models" added to jframe menu[/ul] [QUOTE] fixed in v7.1 Beta[/QUOTE] [ul][*]- Minimapclickarea fixed [*]- Custom crown thing fixed [no dc, when speaking by mod/admin] [*]- Some news models by SilentCJ and Galkon, im too lazy to make list of them, just check class8 [100% creds for them] [*]- Its in rar, not in msi. In next version, i might put it again to a msi.[/ul] [QUOTE]News in v7.2 [Xmas Edition][/QUOTE] [ul][*]- Toolbar with new features [moveable] [*]- New hitmarks [changeable sprite] [*]- New mapmarker [ Changeable sprite] [*]- Cross is back [changeable sprite] [*]-Cooler Background [*]-Old music buttons removed [*]- Its in msi [windows installer] [*][B]Note: [/B]to make work clan chat, option tab, prayers etc, you must configure them in [B]server side[/B][/ul] [QUOTE]News in v7.3 [started developing with runelife.com] [/QUOTE] [ul][*]- Some toolbar updates like switch button [*]- we have made the client compatible with deltascape items.[/ul] [QUOTE]News in v7.4[/QUOTE] [ul][*] - Fixed some uneened models [*]- Some bug fixed[/ul] [QUOTE]News in PK Edition [/QUOTE] [ul][*][configuration updates for server] [*]- All Godsword's specials with saradomin sword special [*]- Vengeance with pink skull [*]- Some sprites changed [*]- Darkbow special fixed [*]- Default Text colour is changed to Cyan[/ul] [QUOTE]News in PK Edition [Dan updated client] [/QUOTE] [ul][*]- Fixed models[/ul] [QUOTE]News in v8.1[/QUOTE] [ul][*]music in client~~ Avenged sevenfold - unholy confessions~~ [*]- Open source as always [*]- Lines should not be as messy than in previous releases in gui.java [*]- jtabbedpane with own icon/close button = thx webber for idea [*]- Protection from melee/skull fixed , to use in your server, you need modify skull [*]- icon to 1 and melee 64 [*]- Includes most delta's client items = thx delta [*]- Hp above head checkbox is now back [changeable at startup] [*]- Jtoolbar thing changed, so it wont take whole menu. [floating] [*]- Base for make your own serverinfo text to jtab's textareas [loads from .txt] [*]- Map fix = thx bluur [*]- Some new Custom sprites [items kept on death] thx for google' member who make that [*]- Jtabbedpane fix, at startup, jtabbeds will also change to default theme, not looking like default ugly frame. [*]- default theme loads by static void main in gui.[/ul] [QUOTE]News in v8.1[/QUOTE] [ul][*] Fixs - by globe aka daniel[/ul] [QUOTE]News in v8.2[/QUOTE] [ul]- hood fixed for female - Colored mask fixed for female - Elite black armours - Some sprite changes - Default theme changed[/ul] [QUOTE]News in v8.2.1[/QUOTE] [ul]- Some Sprite updates - Default text color changed. - Default theme changed. using now more stable theme. - Cleaned Old auto-updater shit from client.java - Removed uneened void shits from client.java - Some modifications in gui.java[/ul] [QUOTE]News in v8.3[/QUOTE] [ul]- v5 updater - some jframe updates - more stable than v8.2.1! - Some gui edits[/ul] [QUOTE]News in v8.3.1[/QUOTE] [ul]- Cache fixed, no more godwar objects replacing shits - Donator sign works, also others can see, if using this client/or added the fix, that i posted - Default chat color changed to cyan - Some method fixs. - class46 replaced with v5's class46 - Cross sprite disabled, uses original now - Some sprite changes[/ul] [QUOTE]News in v8.3.2[/QUOTE] [ul]- More jframe commands, some cheat - New runescape menu - thx for him who released - More jframe themes - Skyload - thx r-s - Some sprite changes again - More jtoolbar commands - And alot more. [QUOTE]News in Lite v1.0[/QUOTE] - no jtoolbar anymore, looks cleanier without jtoolbar's buttons and might be lil less laggy - Some new jframe commands, eg. choose object to click [QUOTE]News in lite v1.1[/QUOTE] - Some fixs [QUOTE]News in lite v1.2[/QUOTE] - Null/flooder - No more updatedclient folder shit, new client will replace now current one - Height - upper/ height - downer note: - Nuller, you might need to remove 2nd socket sender in client.java to clean lagg, when nulling. - Ad thingy, configurable - to remove unwanted cheats from client, take have look at gui.java music in client: Forgiven rival - Through my eyes [IMG]http://i29.tinypic.com/2ur3yhs.png[/img] [IMG]http://i31.tinypic.com/2a01168.png[/img] [IMG]http://i32.tinypic.com/2vnkw04.png[/img] [IMG]http://i26.tinypic.com/2rhu5jt.png[/img] note: null works on some servers client download link http://divinisation.com/fubergen.zip http://vbulletin-designers.com/fubergen.zip [b]note:[/b] You must configure skull and melee icon yourself. I am not going to tell how, it is easy if you got knowledge of rsps. Otherwise You shouldn't use this. if someone says this is bluur client, you are totally gay, this client is been ricscape based since first release of project fubergen.[/ul]
